        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6283161540615?text=Halo%20ONdev%2C%20saya%20mau%20*titip%20belanja*.%0A%0A🛒%20Toko%2Ftempat%20belanja%3A%20%0A🛍️%20Barang%20yang%20dibeli%3A%20%0A📍%20Diantar%20ke%3A%20" class="menu-card" target="_blank">
            <div class="menu-icon"><i class="fas fa-shopping-basket"></i></div>
